I have 3 different Vietnamese writers featured on my website. I am extremely proud to know KyAnh D Phan who has translated 2 of the stories and has also contributed a short essay of his own. He spends much of his time teaching computer skills to Vietnamese refugees. <br><br>
Memories of my combat experience will always be bad. <br>
